verbose_text: Similarly, NF-kappaB p65 activation levels for the 3 g + GdCl 3, 3 g + streptomycin, and 3 g + SN50 groups were 1.39 +/-0.34-fold, 1.42 +/-0.45-fold, and 1.03 +/-0.17-fold, respectively, and were not significantly different from the basal level (n = 5, P> 0.05) (XREF_FIG, XREF_TABLE).
